Tile Company has been approved by Sir Bryan Carsberg, the Director General
of Fair Trading.
*****
TRAVIS PERKINS has acquired the assets of Rockinghams Garden Centre from the
receiver for Pounds 1.35m. The company's garden centre subsidiary, Kennedys,
has 11 centres. Anticipated sales for 1993 are in excess of Pounds 10m.
