                    EUROPEAN SECTOR PROFITABILITY
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
                                          No of      %
Sector                                      cos   chge
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
Auto parts tyre &amp; rubber                      6  357.7
Electrical equipment                          9  102.9
Investment companies                          2   46.1
