<TP>PEOP  Personnel News.
</TP>
<XX>
People:-
</XX>
<PE>Minford, M Ecomonics Professor Liverpool University (UK).
    Wayne Godfrey Professor of Applied Economics Cambridge
    University (UK).
    Congdon, T Managing Director Lombard Street Research (UK).
    Sentance, A Economics Director Confederation of British
    Industry (UK).
